    • getCommits

      public GitHubAPI.Commits getCommits​(String branch, String user) throws IOException
      Retrieves commits per branch per user.
      • If "user" is empty, retrieves all the commits in the branch.
      • If both parameters are empty, branchName defaults to the main branch.
      • If anything fails, a GitHubAPI.Commits object with no commits is returned.
      Parameters:
      branch - Branch name.
      user - The username of the user in question, can be empty.
      Returns:
      A GitHubAPI.Commits object.
      Throws:
      IOException - If the request fails.
